@@TJvStatusBar
<TITLEIMG TJvStatusBar>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.CommCtrl,JVCL.Bars.Statusbars>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Supports extended features such as hot tracking, and accepts controls dropped on it at design time.
Description
  TJvStatusBar is a class derived from TStatusBar that supports extended features such as hot
  tracking, and accepts controls dropped on it at design time.
  
  Use a TJvStatusBar if you want a status bar that enables hot tracking, or where you can place
  controls on.
  
  You can use OnMouseEnter and OnMouseLeave to alter the status bar's look or behavior, when the user
  moves the mouse pointer over the control.
  
  Property HintColor can be used to set a different color of the Help hint boxes for the status bar.

